<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Dashboard - Pharma Transport</title>
<style>
* {margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
body {font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,sans-serif;background:#f8fafc;color:#1f2937;}
.container {max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;padding:2rem;}
header {display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:2rem;}
h1 {color:#1e40af;font-size:2.5rem;}
.logout-btn {background:#ef4444;color:white;padding:0.75rem 1.5rem;border:none;border-radius:0.5rem;font-weight:600;font-size:1rem;cursor:pointer;}
.logout-btn:hover {background:#dc2626;}
.hero {background:linear-gradient(135deg,#10b981 0%,#059669 100%);color:white;padding:3rem;border-radius:1rem;margin-bottom:2rem;text-align:center;}
.hero h2 {font-size:2.2rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;}
.hero p {font-size:1.3rem;opacity:0.95;}
.features {background:white;padding:2.5rem;border-radius:1rem;box-shadow:0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);}
.features h3 {color:#1e40af;font-size:1.5rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem;}
.grid {display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(260px,1fr));gap:1.5rem;list-style:none;}
.grid li {padding:1.5rem;border-left:5px solid;border-radius:0.5rem;background:#f8fafc;}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
<header>
<h1>Pharma Transport</h1>
<%= button_to "Logout", logout_path, method: :delete, class: "logout-btn" %>
</header>

<div class="hero">
<h2>✅ PRODUCTION LIVE</h2>
<p>Secure pharma logistics platform</p>
</div>

<div class="features">
<h3>Core Features</h3>
<ul class="grid">
<li style="border-color:#10b981;"><strong>📄 Chain of Custody</strong><br>21 CFR Part 11 PDFs</li>
<li style="border-color:#3b82f6;"><strong>💳 Payments</strong><br>Stripe production</li>
<li style="border-color:#f59e0b;"><strong>📍 Real-time GPS</strong><br>Cold chain tracking</li>
<li style="border-color:#8b5cf6;"><strong>🏢 Multi-tenant</strong><br>SaaS ready</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
